PART B : PREVENTION CHECKLIST

Stay Safe Online – Prevention Checklist

- Do not click on suspicious links in emails or messages  
- Always verify the website URL before entering details  
- Never share OTPs, passwords, or banking information  
- Use strong and unique passwords  
- Enable two-factor authentication (2FA)  
- Avoid using public Wi-Fi for financial transactions  
- Regularly update your apps and devices  
- Install antivirus or security software  

Financial / UPI Safety
- Always double-check UPI IDs before sending money  
- Do not accept unknown payment requests  

Reporting Cybercrime
- National Cyber Crime Portal: https://cybercrime.gov.in  
- Helpline Number: 1930  
